{"tid":2392493,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"路透社：中國駭客利用SolarWinds軟體漏洞入侵美國政府","createTime":"2021-02-02T23:29:14.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-03T08:39:51.000Z","uid":204533,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"d44f0ae15781250f0185a4d95c9388522b121099","tid":2392493,"uid":204533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T23:29:14.000Z","msg":"路透社引述知情人士報導，疑似中國駭客利用美國軟體開發公司SolarWinds網路管理軟件Orion一個漏洞，去年協助入侵美國政府電腦。<br />\n<br />\n報導指，<strong><span class=\"red\">聯邦調查局（FBI）人員最近發現農業部屬下國家財務中心（National Finance Center）被駭客入侵，恐怕有數以千計政府員工的資料外洩。暫時還不清楚有多少機構在這次攻擊中受害。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n消息人士指，駭客所用的電腦系統和入侵工具，<strong><span class=\"red\">與中國政府支持的網路間諜所用的一樣。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\nOrion去年12月被揭露遭到大規模駭客攻擊，多達1.8萬SolarWinds公私營客戶遭殃，其中美國商務部、財政部的內部電郵遭駭客監看數月。<br />\n<br />\n兩起駭客攻擊雖然同時進行，但互不相關。兩組駭客所利用的軟體漏洞以至攻擊形式都不同。<br />\n<br />\nSolarWinds表示，得知一個客戶被另一組駭客攻擊，是何方所為未有定論，但強調駭客未進入SolarWinds的內部系統，去年12月已修補Orion漏洞。<br />\n<br />\n前聯邦資訊安全長圖希爾（Gregory Touhill）以賽車「氣流牽引」策略作比喻，指出不同駭客組織先後攻擊同一軟體並不稀奇。<br />\n<br />\n有美國前官員指，駭客入侵NFC後果可大可小，因為NFC負責管理多個政府部門的員工薪酬，包括涉及國安的聯邦調查局、國務院、國土安全部、財政部等，而NFC管有職員的社會安全號碼、電話、電郵、銀行資料等。NFC網站提到他們服務逾160部門，為逾60萬聯邦政府職員提供薪酬服務。（國際中心／綜合外電報導）"},{"pid":"4985efc3ee57cfdb0b79c1d3fc2b12812df5d48a","tid":2392493,"uid":204533,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T23:29:49.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/international/20210203/22KKA5BWGNFQPN3A6ZFSYMXTRE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210203%2F22KKA5BWGNFQPN3A6ZFSYMXTRE%2F&d=FM8PVMPbIH5fyb1BVmxPrZ2AEL7eB1GKmMTTK1c2%2F04%3D&h=0ac2c416\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210203%2F22KKA5BWGNFQPN3A6ZFSYMXTRE%2F&h=9e839959\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/international/20210203/22KKA5BWGNFQPN3A6ZFSYMXTRE/</a>"},{"pid":"cdb7d6bfdf8f548109cb21f1c20842cb8f086d5e","tid":2392493,"uid":61831,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T23:31:03.000Z","msg":"ok，所以？<br />\n可恥？CLS？咁仆街都有？"},{"pid":"26cb972b98ae793dcf4bb21c629514a29a7a8ed9","tid":2392493,"uid":27432,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T23:35:18.000Z","msg":"拜登：要耐心教導不要責怪，中國是好夥伴"},{"pid":"af2877db4ab9ce5375f90e3e7d8d098e5e6e5da1","tid":2392493,"uid":243677,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"26cb972b98ae793dcf4bb21c629514a29a7a8ed9","tid":2392493,"uid":27432,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T23:35:18.000Z","msg":"拜登：要耐心教導不要責怪，中國是好夥伴"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T23:36:46.000Z","msg":"用愛感化對方 叫佢唔好咁做<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/pray.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"374662f33b6df00fec18c5ee425996c2f891e7f6","tid":2392493,"uid":155095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T23:37:28.000Z","msg":"拜登：睇唔到 <img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43cdac4e3d483dfad98d2fe9dc622110edda0862","tid":2392493,"uid":109780,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T23:39:18.000Z","msg":"最好美國繼續乜都唔好做<br />\n我哋中国人統一世界<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"167712ab87b697b74790812d95766ce69297b9bd","tid":2392493,"uid":55458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"43cdac4e3d483dfad98d2fe9dc622110edda0862","tid":2392493,"uid":109780,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T23:39:18.000Z","msg":"最好美國繼續乜都唔好做<br />\n我哋中国人統一世界<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T23:43:04.000Z","msg":"中出曬啲白滑鬼妹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d739396c7fef39fe9e233b035559b371647fdf11","tid":2392493,"uid":26708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T01:06:00.000Z","msg":"點解路透社乜都知"},{"pid":"fb4a8974b5aff8e77ca9a2